description:
&lt;p&gt;Following the recent announcement that NHSE/I’s Primary Care functions will be brought together in a single Primary Care Group within the Primary Care, Community Services and Strategy Directorate, we have an exciting opportunity to join the team as Head of Dental Services. This is an exciting time in primary care, with political priority attached to much of our work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Head of Dental Services team is a key member of the Primary Care Commissioning team, providing leadership around the future of dental commissioning and contract reform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who has;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;significant experience/knowledge of dental service delivery, commissioning and contracting and is committed to improving outcomes for patients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a strong track record of delivering complex programmes including policy design and operational delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a flexible attitude to enable effective working and leadership across the primary care commissioning portfolio – particularly across dentistry and optometry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;highly developed stakeholder management skills and experience of working with senior leads from partner organisations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further information can be found in the attached job description.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Gabi Darby&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Director of Transformation (Primary Care Commissioning)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: gabi.darby@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
